earlier in the afternoon and the other events that happened over
the weekend, that was proba bly one of the more interest ing things
out there.''
</P>
<P>
   It's the same conclusion reached by most other TV news directors
in town. By people who've never been on camera. By people who've
never had someone like Ber nard Adelmo Ortiz try to bring them a
blood red rose. &QL; 
