   RECLAIMING THE SABBATH &QL;
</P>
<P>
   FORT WORTH, Texas _ Work. Children. Dinner. An hour at the gym.
The cellphone that rings as you pull into your driveway. It all
makes carving out a day of rest seem impossible. But a growing
Sabbath movement teaches that reclaiming the Sabbath brings both
physical and spiritual renewal. By SANDY GUERRA-CLINE. Story has
moved in ``l'' lifestyle category. &QL; 
