<P>
   RUSSIA-VICTORY (Moscow) _ Celebrating a holiday that defies
ideology, Russians mark Victory Day _ over Nazi Germany _ with a
parade that has World War II veterans marching cheerfully alongside
soldiers of today's Russian Army. President Putin basks in the glow
and promises to bolster the military. By David Filipov. 900 words.
</P>
