</P>
<P>
   &LR; ``You have to put love in food. If it's not there, &LR; 
 &LR; something's missing. Our fish soup is a test of how we're &LR; 
 &LR; feeling that day. We can gauge how much love we've put into the &LR; 
 &LR; food by that dish.'' &LR;
