<P>
   BUSH-McCAIN (Pittsburgh) _ Two months after their bitter primary
battle, John McCain endorses George W. Bush and says he looks
forward to ``enthusiastically campaigning'' for the likely
Republican presidential nominee. McCain, however, asked not to be
considered as a running mate. BY CRAGG HINES and CLAY ROBISON.
