was diagnosed with the same disease last month, and Safir's wife
Carol, were at his side as he made the announcement. (Richard
Perry/The New York Times)
</P>
<P>
   (NYT10) UNDATED -- May 9, 2000 -- WINE-BOTTLE-OPENER -- Opening
a bottle of wine usually entails lots of yanking and tugging at a
